title: What Did the Obama White House Know & When Did They Know it? (Ep 1236)
description:
In this episode, I address the stunning new revelation about this key Spygate plotter which could implicate the Obama White House. I also address two new fake news stories being pushed by the media which have been entirely debunked. 

News Picks:

Stunningly high reported infection rates in NY reflects uncertainty about the Wuhan Virus. 

No, blue states do not subsidize red states. This is a liberal myth. 


Astonishing new study indicated that up to a quarter of NY state residents have Wuhan Virus antibodies. 


Did John Brennan bury evidence that Putin favored Hillary?


Explosive new details emerge about the fake dossier. 

John Durham expands his investigative team looking into the Spygate debacle.

Vaccine expert says he was fired for criticizing Hydroxychloroquine, but there’s more to the story. 

The liberal media gets caught pumping another fake news story about an FDA official and hydroxychloroquine. 

Joy Reid gets caught lying, again.
